An attractive, alluring woman in her early 30's. She is married to James Crane. Their marriage has hit a rough patch as James believes Evelyn is being unfaithful. He suspects she is cheating on him with his brother David. Evelyn is actually keeping a dark secret from her husband; she was once part of the criminal underworld. The actor must be comfortable lying in fake blood for long periods of time.

Audition for roles in movies, television shows, local productions, and more now, using your webcam.
Create casting calls, receive video auditions from actors, and more, without leaving your computer.
Directors fill out a form to create a casting call.
Actors browse casting calls, searching by location and keyword.
When an actor finds a casting call of interest, he or she uses Audition Rocket to record a quick video audition.
The director sees all the video audition submissions, choosing which ones to reject and which ones to send callbacks to.
Actors receive callbacks containing info about their next audition, whether in person or via Audition Rocket.
